ements FixtureAnnotation {\n        private final String value;\n        private final int count;\n\n        private FixtureAnnotationLiteral(String value, int count) {\n            this.value = value;\n            this.count = count;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public String value() {\n            return value;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public int count() {\n            return count;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public Class<? extends java.lang.annotation.Annotation> annotationType() {\n            return FixtureAnnotation.class;\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public boolean equals(Object other) {\n            if (!(other instanceof FixtureAnnotation)) {\n                return false;\n            }\n\n            FixtureAnnotation annotation = (FixtureAnnotation) other;\n            return value.equals(annotation.value()) && count == annotation.count();\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public int hashCode() {\n            return (127 * \"value\".hashCode() ^ value.hashCode())\n                    + (127 * \"count\".hashCode() ^ Integer.valueOf(count).hashCode());\n        }\n    }\n"}]}
[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Evaluating dynamic method invocation**\n\nI'm diving into how invoking an interface method on an object works in a native context. It seems the calling class and agent records are essential. The method invocation looks like methods[i].invoke(obj), but that's based on how the method is declared in `FixtureAnnotation`. Reflecting metadata to handle annotation interface methods is smoother than Class.getAnnotation, which seems to clutter things up. I think editing this for clarity would be a good move!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_06d6a170689c8ed40169f50500c4988193807d43880fb3bd60\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp9QUR41xzQSBNUYyz7uQq_CljJ5nl5JJbPI7WBkg7kS-fRcdApLzDLeFw4VEkR4SUqGt6AVlzUYO3p4-wwvG4Gno0ci_c9OPWwdVhqgBMhnZS5HKY4mHOPs_hwuGL0O9W4aO-k17Jb_clqc2QBFaMEBS07XKq3JWrwVnWbVaoF6hRlaWVzhRUu7_GZWvqsOETz3vqp-pVFUqG2d7ScAwpFl6892GwdxweO_gp6RuNBm3kSWlSe0M_GCdPQXctsrxRRAxOZmLYTcMjXg1b8N1cS25d9-DUgQO1swaCEqCgsOgUaKIybUNk9odk2odMAQZAumhFo5NZzkpaudrj4DJ9PLWbnzH7cnbekDwi2F2VhOgzJ515br07cH6bwycGL5gyKje286qnPZ-YqYGcYhff4zw4PjGJSCTKA9Sml9q2y1F5fNE8J0HHD7qw2jg-Mebz2tHOcpPQ8hBxS69E5ryxwABDaPzpl-k65hgOtsgge80Ui6vSFDRKO_XZx1mOQStrr0sjV2oSrbwkVWAiaNTJ3RQVnkUKeAqexJ8U4X88DrZMH3pBdPgNTi3sy2DdZ-BM9BIvV3oBJOJ0VlRPCafFTyN9eEg8hwAVp7bv1Ki5-Z2dY6t90tVNeJ4LfMfvV8JPdbENBii83-4DeA8C-FaGTfed3ISjCsGpRri-VTKJympACc8f659oQyFs88lW0QeXS1VWEsm6mu6_Dx5lYtE92nFYY9DZrnDQ-BoZDdWVBfV6e09JOavR_q8AU2LeV9-PAYrL8NgQYA8PYuumu0kRqDXsoty-Ne11FpDkiylXzITGNKLFz1k1HisUi1zH2ixUFpjSaxMPq9y-cw0HeEv6Cq84XYkjMp1CKdYFGR9b1WrEemnPSQHyJQiXp2Qn_CUypOf9iErpRv1KvuzbuAmsJ3mBULAxVfrKVXZerq4roQ04uQUCZKrUnOH4hOAjLu4RDt_Uo-ZH1YuqjAk2HWomXVRRin1g9m7uRTp_N3fbW6qVx82BbVoj1mfUWcI1GXe7bxPbyZeH8mjvLi8K-8r6Y1rQAE_cmW6LUqYvmxO_88-RVfRb4-z8gdOgR3itk7v5pRufn5xiN5aumZ96CZHm0zDanVDkTxsIOLWV0ztNIbTRJkyywGxEPSZ0PsfVW-WumkU-Vj___zdZ9bhDvielZ-dnb8BZcIcCeh81iZw8lz55bUd2Tv4cewHNjGJlZ8WhA2LpI6Dty2GV4XAAVkPER9